      "content": "i dont even know why im messaging u. everything just feels so heavy. i cant believe it’s actually over. 10 years... gone. i woke up today and for a split second i forgot, and then it hit me all over again. i dont think i can do this. the thought of having to face another morning without them... i just can't. it feels impossible.",
