      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"moving forward\" sounds so exhausting. every time i think about the future, it just looks like more of this. more emptiness. what if i don't want to live with it? what if the only way to actually stop the hurting is to just... stop everything? it feels like the only permanent way to find any kind of quiet.",
